data.desc: Hello, I'm Wahyu Nusantara. I'm a fresh graduate from AMIKOM University Yogyakarta. With a background in UI/UX design, 3D Modeling, Game development, and Web development, I have a great interest in the world of programming. My expertise spans various span and frameworks, including C#, JavaScript, PHP, Laravel, React.js, and Express.js. Additionally, I am proficient in managing data structure.
